Preconditions:
The input grid must not be null.
The input grid must have at least one row and one column.
The row and col parameters must be valid indices within the grid.
The color parameter must be a valid color value.

Postconditions:
The final grid returned must have the same dimensions as the input grid.
The cell at the specified row and col in the final grid must have the color value specified.
The color of the border cells in the final grid must be modified according to the specified rules.
All other cells in the final grid must have the same color values as the corresponding cells in the input grid.